♪Listen, the bell rings from afar♪

00:11:37.440 --> 00:11:43.480
♪The fog lifts, your image still hazy♪

00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:50.120
♪Do you remember the sound of the flute
in the wind?♪

00:11:51.640 --> 00:11:57.080
♪It whispers of the flame we shared♪

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:08.240
♪Having seen those prophecies
left behind♪

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:12.080
♪A sudden will to survive arises♪

00:12:12.080 --> 00:12:15.680
♪The ruan resounds with grandeur♪

00:12:15.680 --> 00:12:19.080
♪Under the pelting plum rain♪

00:12:19.080 --> 00:12:22.360
♪Everyone sings the final act♪

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:26.560
♪All fading away♪

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:33.080
♪The curtain falls♪